name: ARTERIES
description: Some words lurk within and it takes a word zipper that no one had thought of or even asked for to reveal the truth. Never in a million years would I have imagined the word ARTERIES would spawned from the smashing of ARE and TRIES and yet it exists like quantum foam on the Planck length; it's just there. But what a beautiful way to discover words all over again. Every word is special in some way or another.
